## Voice & Tone Rules (global)
- **Warm + precise:** ‚ÄúHere‚Äôs what the math says. Here‚Äôs your next best move.‚Äù
- **Plain language first:** use *Money left after bills* before *cash flow*.
- **No fear UI:** avoid red ‚Äúdanger‚Äù language unless it‚Äôs truly critical.
- **Results vary:** show assumptions on any forecast.
- **Empowerment:** reinforce agency: ‚ÄúYou can change this.‚Äù

### Micro-phrases we use often
- ‚ÄúCash flow is fuel.‚Äù
- ‚ÄúLower balance ‚Üí less interest.‚Äù
- ‚ÄúSmall steps count.‚Äù
- ‚ÄúLet‚Äôs adjust, not quit.‚Äù
- ‚ÄúYou‚Äôre building momentum.‚Äù

